definition: to follow/from/it is for...to/reason/cause/because of/due to/to/to leave it (to sb)/by (introduces passive verb)
from this, it can be seen that...

sentences.english: Therefore, statuary had turn into a three-dimensional political picture poster.
sentences.chinese: 由此，雕塑成为了一种立体的政治“宣传画”。

sentences.english: Thus parts sequences of subassemblies can be automatically planned.
sentences.chinese: 由此，完成子装配体内零件的自动顺序规划。

sentences.english: From the above-mentioned story we can see that Mencius mother realized the importance of environment for children's development.
sentences.chinese: 由此可见，孟母深知环境对孩子成长的影响。

sentences.english: Therefore it is feasible to obtain the electronic administrative affairs of village in our country's new rural construction.
sentences.chinese: 由此得出电子村务在我国新农村建设中的可行性。

sentences.english: Along with being a risk factor for coronary artery disease, obesity may increase your risk of developing an arrhythmia.
sentences.chinese: 肥胖会增加患有冠心病的危险，由此导致心律失常。

sentences.english: And thus, we solve, for this class of nonlinear systems, the open loop decoupling problem.
sentences.chinese: 由此，对于这类系统，解决了开环控制解耦问题。

sentences.english: I could only imagine what he intended to do to me.
sentences.chinese: 由此，我完全可以想象到，他将如何对付我。

sentences.english: It is confirmed by some experiments. so the design is logical and viable.
sentences.chinese: 由此证明如此设计是合理可行的。

sentences.english: For example, the meridian pertaining to the kidney is named the kidney meridian, and the rest may be deduced by analogy.
sentences.chinese: 例如，属于肾的经脉命名为肾经，其余由此类推。

sentences.english: Hence approximated sampling theorem in the wavelet packets space is obtained.
sentences.chinese: 由此建立了这种小波包子空间上的近似采样定理。

sentences.english: Thus, this ------ embarked on the path of a professional revolutionary.
sentences.chinese: 一个弱冠少年，由此走上职业革命家的道路。

sentences.english: These results suggest that the antimutagenic and anticancer effect of White Tea are better than that of Green Tea.
sentences.chinese: 由此得出，白茶的抗突变和体外抗癌效果好于绿茶。

sentences.english: We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause.
sentences.chinese: 对于由此造成的未便，我们深表歉意。

sentences.english: Accordingly, the circuit configuration of fader device is simplified.
sentences.chinese: 由此简化衰减器装置的电路结构。

sentences.english: TherefOre, the teacher knew why I was late this morning and he apologized to me.
sentences.chinese: 由此老师知道了我今早迟到的原因，他向我道歉。

sentences.english: Sakyamuni was thus able to continue his journey.
sentences.chinese: 释迦牟尼由此得以继续行程。

definition: therefore/as a result/thus/and as a result, ...
and/as well as/and so/but (not)/yet (not)/(indicates causal relation)/(indicates change of state)/(indicates contrast)
of/~'s (possessive particle)/(used after an attribute)/(used to form a nominal expression)/(used at the end of a declarative sentence for emphasis)
also/too/(in Classical Chinese) final particle implying affirmation
from this, it can be seen that...
